description:
Are you praying that Jesus comes soon?
The GuZheng cover of “O Come, O Come Emmanuel” by Yu Jun was originally aired at the General Conference Session 2022. She is from China and is part of the Chinese Union Mission of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
SUBSCRIBE to the official Seventh-day Adventist Church channel: https://www.youtube.com/@AdventistOrgChurch 
FOLLOW (song artist): 
Official Website: www.yujunmusic.com 


SONG DETAILS
Music Composer: Traditional Hymn
Arranger/Orchestrator: Yu Jun
Musician: Yu Jun, plays GuZheng( Chinese Zither), Solo
Institution: Shanghai Chinese Seventh-day Adventist Church
